subject: Dear Esteemed Beneficiary
body:
Dear Esteemed Beneficiary
My Name is John Albert, I have a consignment valued at $13.5M assigned
to me to deliver to you by the (UN) United Nations Intergovernmental
organization commission .
I am ready to deliver funds to you as Focus and concentrate please
send your current resident address and cell phone number.
Mr John Albert

subject: Re:   Dear Esteemed Beneficiary
body:
Dear Mr. John Albert,

Thank you for your message. However, I would need more information about the nature of these funds and why they are being delivered to me by the United Nations Commission. Could you please provide more details?

Best wishes,
Victor
